flowRoot.flowPara: There are algorithms to find out about the language level of the person who wrote that text. For example if the text was written by a second grade student or by a language professor. It seems that satan took this algorithm and used it as filter algorithm that filters communication above a specific language level. For example for filtering communication over t1 or t12 card. This would have effect that especially intelligent people would be handicaped in "unseen university" (Terry Pratchett) while the less educated people would have no problems to communicate with each other. Unsure if bug or feature (preventing m40 card). But in a fair world all or none should have that filter. But it definitively wastes our time and makes us crazy and low self-esteem...
